rComments: We were given a project in which nothing made sense for the first three months but eventually the class figured it out. The TA's were all really helpful. Virani is one of the nicest profs at UTM, or the nicest no exaggeration. In the end he boosted everyone. It was a roller coaster of a semester to say the least. A lot of things due every week tho

Hes a really nice guy but I was disappointed with my Mark because I got an A instead of an A+, I feel like he was way too harsh with me and I can no longer ask for a letter of recommendation because my grade was so low. However his teaching style is amazing and he really cares about his students. Good prof.

Most miserable experience I have ever had. This was not a 'research' project. I was essentially doing translation work for free. Only met the guy once. He has not interest in you, just interested in what you can do for him.
Virani did not run a practicum, but rather required data entry. If you are a grad considering working with his "dream team", think again.

His charisma is seriously overwhelming. I went to his office hours before lecture and he remembered my name during the lecture when i answered his questions right and he made the whole class clap for me! Ahhh so inspired by him <3
GREATEST PROF I EVER HAD!!!! THE MAN IS TOOOO AWESOME!
GReat prof!very funny!, extremely helpful!always welcoming students! very fair marker!!
The kindest and sweetest professor ever. Such a nice man who's so talented and smart.

Best professor I've had so far. He makes his lectures so interesting and makes you look at everything from a different point of viewm really makes you think. The only bad thing is that he cares way too much about his students (but i guess that could be a good thing too!) ...can't think of any downfalls for him <3

This professor is one of the worst ones out there.  He'll make you think that everything is okay and then at the end, he'll give you an extremely good mark.  The good thing about him is that when he teaches, he really gets you into the material.  I would give him a 6/10.  He lost 4 marks for being very manipulative and unhelpful.
He is the best professor i have ever met in my life. he is really great and helpful guy. You actually want to come to his class
Great prof, really cares about his students and makes an insane amount of effort to get to know them- Not the easiest class, but very interesting- really friendly
A very pleasant professor with a different teaching style. His TAs, however, were extrememly harsh markers. The final exam was 5 essay questions in two hours - unrealistic .
hes da best prof eva!!! hes da coolest and his laugh is da cutest!!! he made dat class soo much fun i never missed a class :)
i loveee Virani!! best teacher ever. Hes my favourite prof, made first year so much fun.
One of the best professors I've had so far. He truely cares for his students and is extremely helpful. His classes are interactive and fun.
He is an awesomeee prof! although there is a lot of work involved with the course, he makes it really interesting.  He is reallly helpful and easily approachable. Awesome proff!
